<topic id="markdown-actions">
  <title>Actions Available in the Markdown Editor</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Markdown documents<indexterm>Actions in Markdown Editor</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_if3_cgk_54b">Aside from the actions that are available in <ph keyref="product"/> for any type of document
      (such as the actions in the various menus and the common sections of the toolbar), a variety
      of unique actions are also available in the Markdown editor, from the toolbar and contextual
      menu.</p>
    <section id="jats_toolbar_actions">
      <title>Toolbar Actions</title>
      <p id="p_jf3_cgk_54b">The following default actions are available on the Markdown toolbar when editing Markdown
        documents:</p>
      <p id="p_kf3_cgk_54b">
        <dl id="dl_lf3_cgk_54b">
          <dlentry id="dlentry_mf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Heading1_16.png"/>Header (1st Level)</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts an <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/atx-header"
                  ><term>atx-style</term> first-level header</xref> at the cursor position.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_nf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Heading2_16.png"/>Header (2st Level)</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts an <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/atx-header"
                  ><term>atx-style</term> second-level header</xref> at the cursor position.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_of3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Heading3_16.png"/>Header (3rd Level)</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts an <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/atx-header"
                  ><term>atx-style</term> third-level header</xref> at the cursor position.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_pf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/SeparatorHorizontal16.png"/>Horizontal
                Rule</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts a <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/horizontal_rules"
                >horizontal rule </xref> at the cursor position.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_qf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Bold16.gif" id="image_lhk_5jx_sr"/>Bold
                (Strong)</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Marks the selected text with <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/bold"
                >bold</xref>.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_rf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Italic16.png" id="image_abx_kxx_sr"/>Italic
                (Emphasis)</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Marks the selected text with <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/italic"
                >italics</xref>.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_sf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/StrikeThrough16.png"/>Strikethrough</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Marks the selected text with a <xref
                href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/strikethrough">strikethrough</xref>.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_tf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CodeBlock16.png"/>Code Block</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts (or surrounds selected text in) a <xref
                href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/code-blocks">codeblock</xref>.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_uf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Quote16.png"/>Blockquote</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts a <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/blockquotes"
                >blockquote</xref> at the cursor position.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_vf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Link16.png" id="image_m4x_qrn_ps"/>Insert
                Link</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>
              <p id="p_wf3_cgk_54b">Opens the <uicontrol>Insert Link</uicontrol> dialog box that allows you to define a
                  <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/links">link</xref> to insert at the
                cursor position.</p>
              <p id="p_xf3_cgk_54b">
                <fig id="fig_yf3_cgk_54b">
                  <title>Insert Link Dialog Box</title>
                  <image href="../img/Insert_link.png"/>
                </fig>
              </p>
            </dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_zf3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Image16.gif" id="image_p4x_qrn_ps"/>Insert
                Image</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>
              <p id="p_ag3_cgk_54b">Opens the <uicontrol>Insert Image</uicontrol> dialog box that allows you to define
                an <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/images">image</xref> to insert at
                the cursor position. You can type the URL of the image you want to insert or use
                browsing actions in the <uicontrol><image href="../img/BrowseDrop.png"
                    id="image_n4x_qrn_ps"/>Browse</uicontrol> drop-down menu.</p>
              <p id="p_bg3_cgk_54b">
                <fig id="fig_cg3_cgk_54b">
                  <title>Insert Link Dialog Box</title>
                  <image href="../img/md_insert_image.png"/>
                </fig>
              </p>
            </dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="insert-ol-dlentry">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/OrderedList16.png"/>Insert Ordered
              List</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts an <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/ordered-list">ordered
                list</xref> at the cursor position. Three child list items are also automatically
              inserted by default. You can also use this action to convert selected content to an
              ordered list.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_dg3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/UnorderedList16.png"/>Insert Unordered
                List</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts an <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/unordered-list">unordered
                list</xref> at the cursor position. Three child list items are also automatically
              inserted by default. You can also use this action to convert selected content to an
              unordered list.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_eg3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/ProcedureList16.gif"/>Insert Task
              List</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts a <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/task_lists">task
                list</xref> at the cursor position. Three child list items are also automatically
              inserted by default. You can also use this action to convert selected content to a
              task list.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_fg3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Table16.png"/>Insert Table</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts a <xref href="markdown-rules.dita#markdown-rules/tables">table</xref> at the
              cursor position.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="author editor authorEclipse editorEclipse" id="md-tags-display-mode">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsDrop.png" id="image_pmr_mhm_1s"/>Tags Display
                Mode</uicontrol> drop-down menu</dt>
            <dd>
              <p id="p_gg3_cgk_54b">Allows you to control the amount of markup that is displayed in the <i>Preview</i>
                pane and offers the following choices:</p>
              <p id="p_hg3_cgk_54b">
                <dl conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/dl_Tags_Display_Mode" id="dl_wj4_nbf_tpb">
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_xj4_nbf_tpb">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl>
              </p>
            </dd>
          </dlentry>
        </dl>
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="jats_menu_actions">
      <title>Contextual Menu Actions</title>
      <p id="p_qg3_cgk_54b">The following default actions are available in the contextual menu when editing Markdown
        documents:</p>
      <p id="p_rg3_cgk_54b">
        <dl id="dl_sg3_cgk_54b">
          <dlentry id="dlentry_tg3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Cut16.png" id="image_brg_3z1_5r"/>Cut</uicontrol>,
                  <uicontrol><image href="../img/Copy16.png" id="image_sf4_lst_tr"
              />Copy</uicontrol>, <uicontrol><image href="../img/Paste16.png" id="image_cwr_cqt_tr"
                />Paste</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Use these actions to execute the typical editing actions on the currently selected
              content.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="author developer editor json" id="dlentry_ug3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Source</uicontrol> submenu</dt>
            <dd>
              <p id="p_vg3_cgk_54b">This submenu includes the following actions:</p>
              <p id="p_wg3_cgk_54b">
                <dl id="dl_xg3_cgk_54b">
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_yg3_cgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>To Upper Case</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Converts the content selection to upper case characters.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_zg3_cgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>To Lower Case</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Converts the content selection to lower case characters.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_ah3_cgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Capitalize Lines</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>It capitalizes the first letter found on every new line that is selected.
                      Only the first letter is affected, the rest of the line remains the same. If
                      the first character on the new line is not a letter then no changes are
                      made.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/convert_hex_to_char"
                    id="dlentry_bh3_cgk_54b">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="base64-encode-decode">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Base64 Encode/Decode</uicontrol> submenu</dt>
                    <dd>
                      <p id="p_ch3_cgk_54b">This submenu includes the following actions for encoding
                        or decoding <b>base 64</b> schemes:</p>
                      <p id="p_dh3_cgk_54b">
                        <dl conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/encoding-dl" id="dl_eh3_cgk_54b">
                          <dlentry id="dlentry_fh3_cgk_54b">
                            <dt/>
                            <dd/>
                          </dlentry>
                        </dl>
                      </p>
                    </dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="base32-encode-decode">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Base32 Encode/Decode</uicontrol> submenu</dt>
                    <dd>
                      <p id="p_gh3_cgk_54b">This submenu includes the following actions for encoding
                        or decoding <b>base32</b> schemes:</p>
                      <p id="p_hh3_cgk_54b">
                        <dl conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/encoding-dl" id="dl_ih3_cgk_54b">
                          <dlentry id="dlentry_jh3_cgk_54b">
                            <dt/>
                            <dd/>
                          </dlentry>
                        </dl>
                      </p>
                    </dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="hex-encode-decode">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Hex Encode/Decode</uicontrol> submenu</dt>
                    <dd>
                      <p id="p_kh3_cgk_54b">This submenu includes the following actions for encoding
                        or decoding <b>hex</b> schemes:</p>
                      <p id="p_lh3_cgk_54b">
                        <dl conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/encoding-dl" id="dl_mh3_cgk_54b">
                          <dlentry id="dlentry_nh3_cgk_54b">
                            <dt/>
                            <dd/>
                          </dlentry>
                        </dl>
                      </p>
                    </dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_oh3_cgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Join and Normalize Lines (<shortcut
                          conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/ctrl_j_shortcut"
                      />)</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>For the current selection, this action joins the lines by replacing the
                        <i>line separator</i> with a single space character. It also normalizes the
                      whitespaces by replacing a sequence of such characters with a single
                      space.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_ph3_cgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Insert new line after (<shortcut
                          conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/ctrl_alt_enter_shortcut"
                        />)</uicontrol>
                    </dt>
                    <dd>This action has the same result as moving the cursor to the end of the
                      current line and pressing the <i>ENTER</i> key.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl>
              </p>
            </dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/modify-all-matches"
            product="author developer editor json" id="dlentry_qh3_cgk_54b">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="author developer editor json" id="dlentry_rh3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Open</uicontrol> submenu</dt>
            <dd>
              <p id="p_sh3_cgk_54b">The following actions are available in this submenu:</p>
              <p id="p_th3_cgk_54b">
                <dl id="dl_uh3_cgk_54b">
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/open-file-at-caret-dlentry"
                    id="dlentry_vh3_cgk_54b">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/open-file-in-system-dlentry"
                    id="dlentry_wh3_cgk_54b">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl>
              </p>
            </dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/compare-dlentry"
            product="author developer editor json" id="dlentry_xh3_cgk_54b">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_yh3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Show/Hide Preview</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>A toggle action that shows or hides the <i>Preview</i> pane.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="export-dita">
            <dt><uicontrol>Export as DITA Topic</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Converts the current Markdown document into a DITA topic.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="export-xdita">
            <dt><uicontrol>Export as XDITA Topic</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Converts the current Markdown document into a Lightweight DITA XML topic.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="export-html">
            <dt><uicontrol>Export as HTML</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Converts the current Markdown document into an XHTML document.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_zh3_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Print</uicontrol> (Available in the <i>Preview</i> pane)</dt>
            <dd>Opens a page setup dialog box that allows you to configure printing options for the
              current document.</dd>
          </dlentry>
        </dl>
      </p>
    </section>
